<item>
            <title>[WICKET-5115] ValidationError does not perform variable substitution if setMessage() is used</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5115</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using ValidationError.setMessage() and not using any keys ( setKeys() or addKey() ) the method getErrorMessage() does not perform a variable substitution. The returned string will still containt ${label}&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12639064">WICKET-5115</key>
            <summary>ValidationError does not perform variable substitution if setMessage() is used</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
